{"tid":627073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷40元貨品　休班警務人員被控盜竊","createTime":"2018-04-12T15:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T07:52:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c42ab5523ae677f15971db891af7c2f05c9f130","tid":627073,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"荃灣上月發生店鋪盜竊案，涉案54歲姓沈男警務人員，星期四（12日）正式被控一項盜竊罪。案件將於本月26日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n事發上月14日，荃灣青山公路398號愉景新城商場一間店鋪，保安員報案指一名男子涉嫌盜去一件價值約40元的貨品，警員接到場調查後，沈涉嫌店鋪盜竊被捕，其後案件由新界南總區重案組跟進"},{"pid":"006854b5f73e95cea7dc0e154af333567c049851","tid":627073,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523547791057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523547791057&d=tcVB8DBkPI5NzQNp5hlX67IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=89293175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180412%2Fs00001%2F1523547791057&h=e8b96473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180412/s00001/1523547791057</a>"},{"pid":"941a45c7bbfa6cfac1619b895c2fa88e3775ca86","tid":627073,"uid":36077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:59:08.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"36febdee1fd4d1422b5bec74df38d25928b314f6","tid":627073,"uid":50670,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"GOAL!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"b7f2b6a6e02159198a759507b699545fc9a39490","tid":627073,"uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n</span